"Based on the retrieved posts, social media users are discussing rumors regarding Vladimir Putin's absence, with hashtags such as #putinmissing and #putindead trending. Speculation includes humorous theories about him watching *House of Cards* or preparing for St. Patrick's Day, as well as claims that he has been out of sight for eight days and that his reappearance is a lie. However, one post indicates that he has been seen, suggesting the disappearance may have ended."